ngh (@capt_amarinder) December 6, 2018 Also Read \u2013 MP Farmer Loan Waiver SchemeThe state govt. of Punjab is also committed to waive off loans of landless labourers in the next phases of the implementation of Karza Mafi scheme.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}